{"word":"γόνιμος","slug":"γόνιμος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>γόνιμος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:γονή'><el>γονή</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>productive, fruitful</i>: <el>γ. μέλεα</el> a <i>parent's</i> limbs, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> of persons, <i>genuine</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>; <el>γ. ὕδωρ</el> <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}